CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

October 29, 2008

[Cite as 10/2912008 Case Announcements, 2008-Ohio-5467.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2008-0821. State ex rel. Baldwin v. Hyde.

In Mandamus. On complaint in mandamus of Yvette Barbara Baldwin. On S.Ct.Prac.R. X(5) determination, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., and Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur.
